This paper presents a method for fast inference in Capsule Networks, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks such as image classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of routing coefficients, which are a key component of Capsule Networks, and proposes a method for accumulating and using these coefficients for fast inference. This suggests that the paper may also be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
